headline: Hewlett Packard Enterprise (HPE) Stock Is Up, What You Need To Know
summary: Shares of enterprise technology company Hewlett Packard Enterprise (NYSE:HPE) jumped 4.1% in the morning session after Morgan Stanley upgraded the stock's rating and raised its price target.
